UID:ernest-solvay-fund-2026@artificialnouveau.github.io
DTSTAMP:20260713T112409Z
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20260930
DTEND;VALUE=DATE:20261001
SUMMARY:Deadline: King Baudouin Foundation: Ernest Solvay Fund 2026 (Call f
 or Projects)
DESCRIPTION:The Ernest Solvay Fund provides financial support for local-imp
 act initiatives in three areas: scientific education (science\, technology
 \, engineering and mathematics)\, planet progress (environmental initiativ
 es) and better life (community well-being). ELIGIBILITY: organisations sub
 mitting a project must implement it within a 100 km radius of a Solvay ind
 ustrial\, R&I or administrative site. FUNDING: up to EUR 10\,000 per initi
 ative\; the Fund covers expenses incurred only after the results are annou
 nced (mid-December 2026) and will not reimburse expenses incurred beforeha
 nd. APPLY: create or log in to an account at https://candidate.kbs-frb.be 
 and complete the online application form (it can be saved and completed in
  several stages). Applications are open 15 April 2026 to 30 September 2026
 \; results announced mid-December 2026.\n\nOrganisation: Fonds Ernest Solv
 ay\, managed with the support of the King Baudouin Foundation\nLocation: O
 rganisations implementing a project within a 100 km radius of a Solvay ind
 ustrial\, R&I or administrative site\nAward: Up to EUR 10\,000 per initiat
 ive. Funding covers only expenses incurred after the results are announced
  (mid-December 2026)\; already-incurred expenses are not reimbursed. No ap
 plication fee.\nDuration: Project implemented after mid-December 2026 anno
 uncement\n\nMore: https://kbs-frb.be/en/2026-ernest-solvay-fund?utm_source
 =artificialnouveaugrantdesk&utm_medium=referral
URL:https://kbs-frb.be/en/2026-ernest-solvay-fund?utm_source=artificialnouv
 eaugrantdesk&utm_medium=referral
LOCATION:Organisations implementing a project within a 100 km radius of a S
 olvay industrial\, R&I or administrative site
