 t 15:00 CEST and closes 23 September 2026 at 16:00 CEST. Supports both con
 tent programming and the organisational/curatorial running of a festival\;
  applicants must be organisations rather than individuals\, but the scheme
  is the natural home for any artist-led collective or platform that runs a
